⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Battlefield
node MTG · MTG · ⟦The Battlefield:MTG:11f393⟧

WHO   — The Battlefield — permanents · combat
WHAT  — Where the game is visibly won: creatures attack and block, the board state builds, and the planeswalkers and players take damage.
WHERE — MTG · MTG Arena  Framework inputs: Magic: The Gathering / MTG Arena (WotC)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because for all the depth of the stack, the battlefield is where the duel is embodied and decided.
HOW   — By permanents in play, the combat step, and the slow or sudden swing of the board.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am where it all becomes real — the stack is the argument, but I am the war, and the last life total standing wins on me.

spoken token : kos-nes-vyth   ·   hex : 11f393
